abstract: The 1930 Tudor sedan and its owner were celebrated at the collector car show and auctions in Hershey, Penn., last weekend.
snippet: The 1930 Tudor sedan and its owner were celebrated at the collector car show and auctions in Hershey, Penn., last weekend.
lead_paragraph: After a year of happy rumbling in a 1930 Model A Ford, Jonathan Klinger knew that his return to automotive modernity would be an adjustment.

headline.main: 1930 Model A Ford Wraps a Year on the Road
